  "original_lang": "si",
  "original_title": "\u0dc3\u0dd2\u0dba\u0dbd\u0dd4 \u0db4\u0dcf\u0dc3\u0dbd\u0dca \u0dc3\u0dad\u0dd2\u0dba\u0d9a\u0dca \u0db1\u0dd2\u0dc0\u0dcf\u0da9\u0dd4",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "All schools are off for a week",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The Ministry of Education states that all government schools and government-approved private schools throughout the island will declare the week from tomorrow (4) to the 8th as a holiday week.",
        "This decision was taken in the discussion held today (3) through Zoom technology with officials of the Ministry of Education, Provincial Education Secretaries and Provincial Education Directors.",
        "The Ministry of Education states that this decision was taken after reviewing the progress of the visits of the principals, teachers and students of the schools in the last two weeks and also taking into consideration the notices of the Ministry of Electricity and Energy regarding the distribution of fuel.",
        "The Ministry of Education also stated in a statement that the school time lost during this week will be covered in the upcoming school vacation season."
      ],
